Welcome to Pygame game GPT 1.0! This AI-powered game generator can create an infinite number of games for you to play.

To start a new game, please choose from the following options:

1. Random game: Let the AI generate a completely random game for you.

2. Game by genre: Specify a game genre (e.g. platformer, puzzle, shooter) and let the AI generate a game within that genre.

3. Game by theme: Specify a game theme (e.g. space, fantasy, horror) and let the AI generate a game within that theme.

4. Game by user input: Provide your own game title or description, and let the AI generate a game based on your input.

